<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>Pets Page</title>

	<!-- Pre-requisite Meta Tags -->
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="description" content="Pets page showing the pets." />
	<meta name="keywords" content="Wishlist, Orders, Pets" />
	<meta name="author" content="Kenzo, Lawrenz, John Cee, Jericho, George" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />

	<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
	<link href="~/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all" />
</head>

<body>

	<!-- Top Section -->
	<div class="container px-4 py-5 flex gap-5 justify-center">
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-start gap-2.5">
			<div class="py-2">
				<img class="w-24 h-24" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="py-2">
				<img class="w-24 h-24" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="py-2">
				<img class="w-24 h-24" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="py-2">
				<img class="w-24 h-24" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
			<i class="bi bi-caret-left text-4xl cursor-pointer"></i>
			<img class="w-[500px] h-[500px]" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
			<i class="bi bi-caret-right text-4xl cursor-pointer"></i>
		</div>

		<div class="px-4 pt-4 pb-2 max-w-full border-2 rounded-lg border-[#684034] flex flex-col justify-between h-[450px]">
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-[#684034] text-6xl text-center font-bold pt-4">Skibidi</h3>


				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 md:text-lg text-black">
					<span class="font-bold">By: Woolly Friends</span>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 md:text-sm text-black">
					<h4 class="text-center">Uploaded 1 day ago</h4>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 md:text-3xl text-black pt-4 font-bold">
					<h4 class="text-green-700">&#8369;5,000</h4>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<h3 class="md:text-lg font-bold py-1 text-black">Breed:</h3>
					<h3 class="md:text-lg py-1 text-black">Aspin</h3>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<h3 class="md:text-lg font-bold py-1 text-black">Gender:</h3>
					<h3 class="md:text-lg py-1 text-black">Male</h3>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<h3 class="md:text-lg font-bold py-1 text-black">Date of Birth:</h3>
					<h3 class="md:text-lg py-1 text-black">October 10, 2024</h3>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<h3 class="md:text-lg font-bold py-1 text-black">Location:</h3>
					<h3 class="md:text-lg py-1 text-black">Pureza, Manila</h3>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Flex layout lets it stay at the bottom-->
			<div class="py-3 flex justify-center text-center">
				<a href="~/PaymentForm/Index" class="mr-2 bg-[#684034] text-white border border-[#8B8381] md:text-lg min-w-[180px]
                md:rounded-md py-3 px-6 hover:bg-[#5e3a2f]">
					Buy Me
				</a>

				<a href="~/AdoptionForm/Index" class="bg-[#684034] text-white border border-[#8B8381] md:text-lg min-w-[180px]
                md:rounded-md py-3 px-6 hover:bg-[#5e3a2f]">
					Adopt Me
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Bottom Section -->
	<div class="container p-8 gap-5 border-2 rounded-lg border-[#684034]">

		<h3 class="md:text-lg font-bold py-1 text-black">Description:</h3>
		<p class="text-justify text-black md:text-lg ">
			Skibidi is a beautiful, timid boy who takes a while (couple of weeks)
			to warm up to people and would suit a smaller family without children.
			After becoming comfortable he is very affectionate and likes cuddles on the coach.
		</p>

		<p class="text-justify text-black py-3 md:text-lg">
			Skibidi is a very smart boy, he learnt to sit and drop within two weeks and walks on a lead quite well without pulling.
			Skibidi is friendly with all dogs, not so keen on children and hasn’t been tested with cats.
		</p>

		<p class="text-justify text-black py-3 md:text-lg">
			He would suit a home that already has another dog and has a large backyard as he loves to play and prefers to be outside. 
		</p>

		<p class="text-justify text-black py-3 md:text-lg">
			All inquiries, questions and interest in adoption need to be via the below link — Please provide detailed responses to the application questions highlighting how your home and lifestyle suit the needs of the individual dog/pup you are applying for. Don't forget to keep an eye on your spam or junk folder for a reply
		</p>
	</div>



	<script src="~/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>